    <Title><![CDATA[The example explained]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The example adds a new app category "Example Apps" with the apps "List" and "Form". While "Form" documents the main features for workplace apps in a very simple way without any "useful" functionality, the "List" app displays a list of resources in the same way the explorer does and you can operate on these resources the same way.</p>]]></content>
